sequenceDiagram
    participant Kafka as Kafka Broker<br/>dev.aihub-public-*<br/>9096/TCP SASL_SSL
    participant KProc as kafka-processor<br/>Python Consumer
    participant VHub as model-validation-hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant AClient as api-client<br/>Python HTTP Client
    participant FS as Local Filesystem<br/>data/ directory
    participant Git as Git Repository
    participant Konflux as Konflux Build<br/>Dockerfile.konflux
    participant Registry as Container Registry<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant InitC as Init Container<br/>/app/benchmarks
    participant Volume as Shared emptyDir<br/>Volume
    participant MCatalog as model-catalog<br/>Service

    rect rgb(230, 245, 230)
        Note over Kafka,FS: Flow 1: Kafka Data Ingestion (Dev/Build Time)
        Kafka->>KProc: CDC messages (Debezium)<br/>SASL_SSL / SCRAM-SHA-512
        KProc->>KProc: Process CDC envelopes<br/>Dedup, accuracy calc,<br/>hardware config enrichment
        KProc->>FS: Write JSON/NDJSON<br/>provider/model hierarchy
    end

    rect rgb(230, 235, 250)
        Note over VHub,FS: Flow 2: API Data Ingestion (Dev/Build Time)
        AClient->>VHub: GET /api/v1/{providers,models,...}<br/>TLS (custom CA cert)
        VHub-->>AClient: Paginated JSON responses
        AClient->>AClient: Post-process<br/>Dedup, accuracy calc,<br/>hardware config enrichment
        AClient->>FS: Write JSON/NDJSON<br/>(identical to kafka output)
    end

    rect rgb(250, 245, 230)
        Note over FS,Registry: Build Pipeline
        FS->>Git: git commit + push data/
        Git->>Konflux: Trigger build
        Konflux->>Konflux: COPY data/ → /app/benchmarks<br/>UBI9-minimal base
        Konflux->>Registry: Push container image
    end

    rect rgb(245, 230, 230)
        Note over Registry,MCatalog: Flow 3: Runtime Data Delivery (Cluster)
        Registry->>InitC: Pull init container image<br/>HTTPS/443, Registry auth
        InitC->>Volume: Copy /app/benchmarks<br/>to shared emptyDir
        Volume->>MCatalog: Read benchmark data<br/>JSON/NDJSON files
    end
